  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer Barbarians</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They attacked Your village, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They killed Your family. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab Your sword and Go get 'em!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a challenging Hack & Slash game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer or Single Player Modes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level-up System</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inventory System</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advanced A.I. Enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stealth Kill</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Menus -</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Network connection</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay, controls, graphics, and audio settings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and much more…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* This game is part of the \"Hack & Slash\" mini-series event from Archor Games, be sure to check it out on Steam! *</p>",
